{
  "$schema": "./contract.schema.json",
  "id": "mui.chip",
  "name": "Chip",
  "version": "0.2.0",
  "status": "draft",
  "description": "SEED contract for the MUI computed-floor round — props/axes only; anatomy is promoted from captured DOM truth (Round 4). Subject: @mui/material@9.2.0 (pinned, examples/mui/PROVENANCE.md). COMPUTED-ENRICHED (extract/computed): unlabeled styled channels minted from computed-style capture of @mui/material@9.2.0 in headless Chromium 149.0.7827.55; overflow channels in the sibling extension file. FLOOR-PROMOTED (examples/mui/scripts/promote-floor.mjs): enriched.contract.json — computed-capture truth; minted leaves source-aliased to MUI's own CSS-variable references where verified (source-bindings.json); extension sidecar carries the named overflow.",
